1) Read INSTALL file and install all the dependencies
2)make config
3) cd src/Devices
4) edit Makefile add XVAVI.o to 
	OBJS = XVPwc.o XVV4L2.o XVBt8x8.o Meteor.o XVDig1394.o XVFlea2G.o \
                   XVImageSeq.o XVVideo.o XVMpeg.o
           at the end
           
5) cd ../..
6) make
7)sudo make install        
               
